snippet.title: Sharing on AnVIL
snippet.description:
This video will give you a quick introduction to the AnVIL project and how easy it makes it to share data, code, and workflows among collaborators.

Check out the Getting Started Guide here: https://jhudatascience.org/AnVIL_Book_Getting_Started/

You can see the slides for this video here: https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1IOOzvnKoTMJdRLFjCup_9FqQpumP07NwoBb9mIlD7lM/edit?usp=sharing.

SRA on AnVIL Guide: https://hutchdatascience.org/AnVIL_SRA_Data/ 

Check out the Getting Started Guide here: https://jhudatascience.org/AnVIL_Book_Getting_Started/

You can see the slides for this video here: https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1bp5zlltpT9HYzm6aBYY8XBoleQ7nrTQNTK34-2Xz6Tg/edit?usp=sharing.
